### RTO Service API Tests

### 1. Verify Valid Vehicle (Maharashtra)
POST http://localhost:8085/api/v1/rto/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "registrationNumber": "MH12AB1234",
  "rtoCode": "MH12",
  "manufacturer": "Maruti Suzuki",
  "model": "Swift",
  "year": 2020,
  "fuelType": "PETROL"
}

### 2. Verify Valid Vehicle (Delhi)
POST http://localhost:8085/api/v1/rto/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "registrationNumber": "DL01CA5678",
  "rtoCode": "DL01",
  "manufacturer": "Hyundai",
  "model": "Creta",
  "year": 2021,
  "fuelType": "DIESEL"
}

### 3. Verify Valid Vehicle (Karnataka)
POST http://localhost:8085/api/v1/rto/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "registrationNumber": "KA05MN9876",
  "rtoCode": "KA05",
  "manufacturer": "Honda",
  "model": "City",
  "year": 2019,
  "fuelType": "PETROL"
