### 4. Verify Invalid Vehicle (Wrong Format)
POST http://localhost:8085/api/v1/rto/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "registrationNumber": "INVALID123",
  "rtoCode": "XX99",
  "manufacturer": "Test",
  "model": "Test",
  "year": 2020,
  "fuelType": "PETROL"
}

### 5. Get Verification by Registration Number
GET http://localhost:8085/api/v1/rto/verify/MH12AB1234

### 6. Get Verification by Registration Number (Delhi)
GET http://localhost:8085/api/v1/rto/verify/DL01CA5678

### 7. Verify Electric Vehicle
POST http://localhost:8085/api/v1/rto/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "registrationNumber": "TN09EV1234",
  "rtoCode": "TN09",
  "manufacturer": "Tata",
  "model": "Nexon EV",
  "year": 2022,
  "fuelType": "ELECTRIC"
}
